    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97 I am so excited to list my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about keeping it spotless, so it\u2019s basically perfect inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been totally pampered and is ready for a new adventure, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to message me, I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
