      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely spotless inside and out! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays in perfect shape. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh feel to it. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
