      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a superlative example of the marque, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a documented VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, delivering power to the rear wheels via the factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis remains flawlessly balanced, retaining its original suspension geometry and bushing integrity. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the paint retains full depth with zero clear coat failure, while the interior Nappa leather shows no bolster wear or UV damage. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver for the technical purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
